            "description": "Alias resource record sets only: Information about the Amazon Web Services resource, such as a CloudFront distribution or an Amazon S3 bucket, that you want to route traffic to. \n When creating resource record sets for a private hosted zone, note the following: \n * For information about creating failover resource record sets in a private hosted zone, see Configuring Failover in a Private Hosted Zone (https://docs.aws.amazon.com/Route53/latest/DeveloperGuide/dns-failover-private-hosted-zones.html).",
